  "title": "Auxiliary Police Officer X 6 - Various Location (Training & Allowances Provided)",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Permanent Full Time</strong></li><li><strong>Basic $3100 to $5070 + Shift allowances + Join Bonuses ($15000 to $45000)</strong></li><li><strong>Working location: Island Wide, Singapore</strong></li><li><strong>12 hours shift (Morning / Night)</strong></li><li><strong>Full Training Provided (Training allowances provided)</strong></li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><p><br /></p><ul><li><strong>Protection and Escorting:</strong> Provide protection and escort services for VIPs and business partners.</li><li><strong>Security Enforcement:</strong> Conduct security enforcement and screening duties to maintain a safe environment.</li><li><strong>Traffic and Crowd Control:</strong> Manage traffic flow, crowd control, and access control to ensure public safety and order.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Strong communication and interpersonal skills.</li><li>Ability to remain calm and composed in stressful situations.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now button</strong> with the following information in the resume</p><ul><li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li><li>Current and Expected salary</li><li>Reason for leaving</li><li>Date of availability</li><li>Education background</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>Barry Ang Ze Xin (Reg No : R26159529)</p><p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
